<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resend Verification - Eascap</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=MuseoModerno:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 1.6;">

  <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 24px 10px;">
        
        <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #333C4D; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
          
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 45px 20px; background-color: #314E82;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 48px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'MuseoModerno', 'Arial Black', sans-serif;">
                EASCAP
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
              <h2 style="color: #062837; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 0; font-weight: 700;">Email Verification</h2>
              
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333;">Hello Eascaper,</p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333; text-align: justify;">
                We received a request to resend the verification link for your <strong>Eascap</strong> account. To ensure your security and gain full access to our community, please confirm your email address below.
              </p>

              <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                    <a href="{{VerificationLink}}" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 32px; background-color: #314E82; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px;">
                      Verify Email Address
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333; text-align: justify;">
                Once verified, you can resume browsing properties and managing your bookings.
              </p>

              <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px; background-color: #FFE6F0; border-left: 4px solid #FFC2C2; border-radius: 4px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #062837; line-height: 1.4;">
                  <strong>Quick Note:</strong> This verification link will expire in 1 hour. If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it; no changes will be made to your account.
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 16px; color: #333333;">
                Kind regards,<br />
                <strong style="color: #314E82;">The Eascap Team</strong>
              </p>
              
              <h2 style="color: #314E82; margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-family: 'MuseoModerno', 'Arial Black', sans-serif; font-size: 24px;">
                Eascap.
              </h2>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px; background-color: #ffffff; border-top: 1px solid #333C4D; text-align: center;">
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #333333;">
                Need help? Contact us at 
                <a href="mailto:eascapteam@eascap.com" style="color: #314E82; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">eascapteam@eascap.com</a>
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #888888;">
                &copy; 2026 Eascap. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>